{"tid":1510470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改歌MV 救香港","createTime":"2019-08-27T07:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T07:59:12.000Z","uid":17501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1be237e3d4268a580c30196365fe20d506c41bf","tid":1510470,"uid":17501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:55:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得比起文字同圖片<br />\n改編歌曲同歌詞更加容易感動人嘅國際文宣<br />\n岩岩睇完巴打改編嘅歌 感動到喊哂口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/rxklxik29p9d/brave-heart\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Frxklxik29p9d%2Fbrave-heart&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=1eac8c4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/rxklxik29p9d/brave-heart</a><br />\n<br />\n如果用同樣方法 改做各國語言（日，普，英，法等）嘅歌詞 內容講番香港人抗爭運動嘅決心，再加埋MV剪接番抗爭畫面，可以好正面咁感染國際嘅人，推使佢地同當地政府介入。<br />\n<br />\n大家不妨推埋呢個post！ 聽下：<br />\n<br />\n【逆權版】數碼暴龍進化歌brave heart<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1473635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1473635</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f09f8e8917b3897e41afb587484352562f85784e","tid":1510470,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/suRKmvs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRKmvs.gif&h=09fb3e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%